Package cthoelken

Class Summary
Alignment Object to keep 2 to n sequences, symbols for matches and mismatches between them and print out the alignment.
Cluster Auxilliary class for tree based clusters in UPGMA and WPGMA
CostMatrix Auxilliary class to store the computed values for two or three sequences
FengDoolittle Implementation of the Feng-Doolittle Algorithm for progressive multiple alignments with linear gap costs.
Gotoh Implementation of the Gotoh Algorithm for pairwise alignments with affine gap costs.
NeedlemanWunsch Implementation of the Needleman Wunsch Algorithm for pairwise alignments with linear gap costs.
PGMA Implementation of the Weighted and Unweighted Pair Group Method using the Arithmetic mean for multiple alignments.
SubstitutionMatrix Substitution Matrix based on PAM250 or BLOSUM62 scores
SumOfPairs Implementation of the Sum-Of-Pairs Algorithm for optimal multiple alignments with linear gap costs.
